==Dialogue==
{{Dialogue Start}}
:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 434182003: Config/Level/Mission/4341820/Act/Act434182003.json-->
:'''Fortuna:''' The darkness... has been driven away. I see many faces, silver-gray in shade. I see a flame, a silver-gray flame... Though dim, it has not gone out.
:'''Fortuna:''' Thank you, kind soul. I feel much warmer now.
:'''Fortuna:''' I would love to hear how you managed it, but I believe you have more important things to do. Go without worry, we will support each other as we wait for the new dawn.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} This is the power of "Trailblaze"!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's time to go and light the other Living Flames.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} With this, all the Living Flames have been ignited.
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_434182307-->
:'''Fortuna:''' Once again, thank you for ensuring that we do not have to wait for the final moment in complete darkness.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_434182003-->
